Rule compilation error starting on line 2 index 3: Name used more than twice

   2| A(name) >< B() =>
        ^~~~
   3|     HelloWorld() ~ Eraser(),
   4| 
   5|     name ~ C(name);
                   ^~~~

Hint: Names should be used exactly twice in one scope. Consider using duplicator agents (Dup2, Dup3, ...).
